                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1400241/">weiwei</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2013-10-28</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">和《弯曲的脊梁》同时签的书，可与《他们以为他们是自由的》对照读，两种视角。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="747767087">
        <div class="comment">
